Welcome to Ultimate Surrender’s 2009 Tag Team League. Team Ice vs Team Ninja. Four girls, non-scripted, real tag team action.

This is the start of the new 2009 Tag Team Season. New teams; new wrestlers. The Beginning of what will be the the most brutal Tag Team Season yet!

Team Ice: Alexa Von Tess has teamed up with rookie sensation Bella Rossi. This team is bigger than all the other teams and has the experience and strength to win it all. When one of these girls drops a booty on your face, you’re going nowhere.

Team Ninja: Vendetta is the Team Captain, and hand picked Kirra Lynne for her partner. Kirra is a true Pit Bull; fast determined and dangerously brutal. However, she lacks mat time, and is the least experienced girl in the league. But with Vendetta on your team, that might not mean much.

This is the first match of the new 2009 Tag Team season: 5 teams battle to see who will be crowned the Champion. If you have not joined yet, now is the time. This is the ground floor of the most brutal sexy wrestling league on the net. Watch it from the start!
